Class ICPBrasilUserHomeProviderCA

java.lang.Object

public class ICPBrasilUserHomeProviderCA extends Object implements org.demoiselle.signer.core.ca.provider.ProviderCA
FIXME each provider should be independent of any other Get the ICP-BRASIL's Trusted Certificate Authority Chain from file (ACcompactado.zip) stored on user home folder, that was previous downloaded by ICPBrasilOnLineSerproProviderCA or ICPBrasilOnLineITIProviderCA.
